    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯或将维持对华关税“连续性”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-23/harris-could-provide-continuity-on-china-tariffs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国官方避免对卡马拉·哈里斯迟迟加入美国总统竞选发表评论。但国家支持的新闻媒体和社交媒体用户认为她是一位软弱的副总统，其候选资格不会对世界第二大经济体构成重大威胁。新美国安全中心兼职高级研究员、Ziemba Insights 创始人 Rachel Ziemba 与 Jennifer Zabasajja 就“中东和非洲视野”进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-23/harris-could-provide-continuity-on-china-tariffs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:06:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国电网运营商申请建设氢气网络许可</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/german-grid-operators-request-permit-to-build-hydrogen-network</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国天然气管网运营商已请求批准建设一条长 10,000 公里（6,214 英里）的氢气网络，首批管道将于明年投入运营。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/german-grid-operators-request-permit-to-build-hydrogen-network</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:04:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰米·戴蒙精心挑选的华尔街双雄追逐更大市场份额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/jamie-dimon-s-handpicked-wall-street-duo-hunts-more-market-share</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一月份的一个周六，其中一人正和家人坐在车里，另一人则关机了。这时，杰米·戴蒙 (Jamie Dimon) 开始拨打他们的电话号码，并问道：他们能否经营一家比高盛 (Goldman Sachs) 规模更大的华尔街公司？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/jamie-dimon-s-handpicked-wall-street-duo-hunts-more-market-share</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博世将以 80 亿美元收购江森自控空调资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/bosch-to-buy-jci-air-conditioning-assets-in-8-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗伯特·博世有限公司 (Robert Bosch GmbH) 计划以 80 亿美元收购江森自控国际有限公司 (Johnson Controls International Plc) 的供暖和通风资产，以扩大其投资组合，不再局限于汽车供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/bosch-to-buy-jci-air-conditioning-assets-in-8-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 08:20:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>昆巴铁矿认为南非新政府愿意进行铁路改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/kumba-iron-ore-sees-new-south-africa-government-open-to-rail-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团南非铁矿石部门表示，该国新政府致力于解决限制出口的物流瓶颈，同时承认这一问题可能需要数年时间才能解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/kumba-iron-ore-sees-new-south-africa-government-open-to-rail-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 08:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度提高资本利得税 股市受挫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/india-to-hike-capital-gains-tax-in-setback-for-stock-market-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度提高了股权投资资本收益税，并提高了股票衍生品交易的征税额，旨在抑制该国 5 万亿美元股市的投机热情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/india-to-hike-capital-gains-tax-in-setback-for-stock-market-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 07:13:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管摩根大通对英镑上涨发出警告，Amundi 仍加入英镑多头行列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/amundi-joins-pound-bulls-even-as-jpmorgan-warns-on-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英镑全球领先的上涨势头已使 Amundi SA 由看跌转为看涨，尽管摩根大通 (JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co.) 警告称，持仓似乎过高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/amundi-joins-pound-bulls-even-as-jpmorgan-warns-on-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
